_sText:
There was one bug in sky scraper v6, a floating light.

Here is the fixed version.



Whats been changed.



The wall around the top of the Sky scraper has been lowerd so that Zombies cannot jump onto the cargo crates.

Added another secret.

Added a ladder to the top of the Destroyable tower that can be pushed off and destroyed.

Fixed the floating light.



Map features.



2 Secrets

Cubemaps

Good Fps

Destroyable tower

70 spawn points
